babel cli - babel command line
    installation: npm i -g babel-cli

installing babel for es6 es7
    - yarn add babel-preset-env
        - the env is the library that works with es5, es6, es7

installing babel for react:
    - yarn add babel-preset-react
    
commands: 
    babel --help > help

compling with babel: 
    - babel <input file> --out-file=<output file> --presets=<wanted presets> --watch(only if we want babel to watch), complete example: 
    - babel states.js --out-file=app.js --presets=env,react --watch
